      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im currently on sertraline (zoloft) for my anxiety but the side effects r making me feel super nauseous and weirdly restless all the time. i was reading online that st johns wort is basically the same thing but just more natural. is it okay if i just swap the zoloft out for the herb starting tomorrow? i dont really want to go back to my doctor for another appointment if i dont have to.",
